{"tid":1798214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★返工=?? 手推車翻側鐵架倒下　76歲男搬運工遭擊中頭部昏迷","createTime":"2019-12-26T05:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T05:54:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d53a75e881b790be4fe39a726eb5263b3cdb8c8","tid":1798214,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"上水寶運路近文閣村，今晨(26日)9時39分，一名姓廖<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(76歲)</span></strong>男工在上址對開做搬運工作期間，其手推車突然翻側，車上一個2米乘2米乘12厘米的鐵架倒下，擊中廖男頭部，他受傷一度陷入昏迷，一旁姓黃(60歲)男工友見狀慌忙報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場，事主其後轉醒，由救護車送往北區醫院治理，經調查後警方相信事件沒有可疑，列作有人意外受傷處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191226/photo/bkn-20191226095427005-1226_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191226121231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191226%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191226095427005-1226_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191226121231&h=21c94d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191226/bkn-20191226095427005-1226_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191226%2Fbkn-20191226095427005-1226_00822_001.html&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=a6188d16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191226/bkn-20191226095427005-1226_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"475ad001d318b7b41777f1df587233713b633303","tid":1798214,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:17:43.000Z","msg":"76歲搬運工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2275ca8cf4011765f02c3d6bb0f6250b2b1a0316","tid":1798214,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":